cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper describes a framework for the development of an integrative cognitive system based on probabilistic generative models. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of automatic speech recognition (ASR) and image data, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper mentions the use of neural network-based modules, which falls under the domain of neural networks (cs.NE).
